msgctxt "RonivansLegacy_ChemicalProcessing.STRINGS.ITEMS.INDUSTRIAL_PRODUCTS.MINING_DRILLBITS_BASIC_ITEM.DESC"
msgid ""
"A set of sturdy drill bits made for basic mining operations.\n"
"Has no own guidance system and can drill through soft rocks stratum."
